"{    \"translations\": [        {            \"english_version\": \"President Joe Biden delivered a passionate speech urging Congress to support Ukraine and stand up to Vladimir Putin. He expressed concern that Russia's aggression would not be limited to Ukraine and called the war in Gaza 'gut-wrenching'. Biden also criticized Donald Trump for being soft on Russia and announced plans to build a temporary pier off Gaza's coast for aid delivery.\",            \"english_title\": \"International Relations and Conflicts\",            \"translated_version\": \"El Presidente Joe Biden dio un discurso apasionado pidiendo al Congreso que apoye a Ucrania y se oponga a Vladimir Putin. Expres\u00f3 preocupaci\u00f3n de que la agresi\u00f3n de Rusia no se limitar\u00eda a Ucrania y llam\u00f3 a la guerra en Gaza 'desgarradora'. Biden tambi\u00e9n critic\u00f3 a Donald Trump por ser suave con Rusia y anunci\u00f3 planes para construir un muelle temporal en la costa de Gaza para la entrega de ayuda.\",            \"translated_title\": \"International Relations and Conflicts\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"Hong Kong introduced a new national-security law with strict provisions including offences like treason and foreign interference. The law is aligned with China's national-security law from 2020. France and Moldova signed economic and defence agreements to counter Russian aggression, while Transnistria sought Kremlin assistance. Canada mourned a tragic attack in Ottawa where six Sri Lankans were stabbed to death.\",            \"english_title\": \"National Security and Legislation\",            \"translated_version\": \"Hong Kong introdujo una nueva ley de seguridad nacional con disposiciones estrictas que incluyen delitos como traici\u00f3n e interferencia extranjera. La ley est\u00e1 alineada con la ley de seguridad nacional de China de 2020. Francia y Moldavia firmaron acuerdos econ\u00f3micos y de defensa para contrarrestar la agresi\u00f3n rusa, mientras que Transnistria busc\u00f3 ayuda del Kremlin. Canad\u00e1 lament\u00f3 un tr\u00e1gico ataque en Ottawa donde seis esrilanqueses fueron apu\u00f1alados hasta la muerte.\",            \"translated_title\": \"National Security and Legislation\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"Former British Prime Minister Theresa May announced her resignation as a Conservative MP to focus on causes like combating modern slavery. Over 60 Conservative MPs have resigned ahead of the upcoming general election. The political landscape in the UK is undergoing significant changes.\",            \"english_title\": \"Political Developments\",            \"translated_version\": \"La ex Primera Ministra Brit\u00e1nica Theresa May anunci\u00f3 su renuncia como diputada conservadora para centrarse en causas como combatir la esclavitud moderna. M\u00e1s de 60 diputados conservadores han renunciado antes de las pr\u00f3ximas elecciones generales. El panorama pol\u00edtico en el Reino Unido est\u00e1 experimentando cambios significativos.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Political Developments\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"Australia's Great Barrier Reef experienced another mass bleaching event due to rising sea temperatures. This marks the fifth instance of damage in eight years, posing a serious threat to the world's largest coral system. The UN has warned about the reef's deteriorating condition.\",            \"english_title\": \"Environmental Concerns\",            \"translated_version\": \"La Gran Barrera de Coral de Australia experiment\u00f3 otro evento de blanqueamiento masivo debido al aumento de las temperaturas del mar. Esto marca la quinta instancia de da\u00f1o en ocho a\u00f1os, representando una seria amenaza para el sistema de coral m\u00e1s grande del mundo. La ONU ha advertido sobre la condici\u00f3n deteriorante del arrecife.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Environmental Concerns\"        }    ]}"